                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> Pressure is applied to the floor tiles</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The trap shoots a wave of darts targeting the entire area as a single attack. Creatures in the affected area take @Damage[(4d8+10)[poison]|traits:nonlethal]{4d8+10 nonlethal poison} poison damage and must attempt a @Check[reflex|dc:21] save. The trap also triggers an audible alarm.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature takes no damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Slowed]{slowed 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage and is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Slowed]{slowed 3}.</p>"
